because I'm afraid!

40
00:02:10.380 --> 00:02:11.856
It's making me!

41
00:02:11.880 --> 00:02:15.356
Whatever is inside
me. it's getting stronger.

42
00:02:15.380 --> 00:02:18.526
Help me. Elgin. I can save all of you.

43
