When I was a little
girl. I saw this place. too.

62
00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:19.716
Anghkooey.

63
00:03:19.740 --> 00:03:21.216
Remember.

64
00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:22.926
God.

65
00:03:22.950 --> 00:03:25.386
The reason I felt what Miranda felt

66
00:03:25.410 --> 00:03:28.056
